uses pdftex.map instead of dvipdfm.map, because the new
dvipdfmx and xdvipdfmx can read map files of dvips format.
The entry in the default pdftex.map is

ptmr8r NimbusRomNo9L-Regu "TeXBase1Encoding ReEncodeFont" <8r.enc <utmr8a.pfb

